data.description:
BOARDMAN SCHOOLS! 
Bring offer on this nice 3 bedroom, 2 bath home before it’s gone!
Large Eat-in Kitchen with appliances, large Living Room, spacious bedrooms, a finished area in basement that owners used as a bedroom, Sunroom overlooking a beautiful inground pool complete with pool accessories, heater, cover, chemicals, and more. 
There are 2 fenced in areas outside of the pool area which would be great for gardens, play areas, areas for pets, and more.
